---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<section id="tools" class="py-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
    <!-- Titre -->
    <h2 class="inline-block text-3xl font-extrabold mb-10 p-4 bg-[#36f4a4]/10 border-2 border-[#36f4a4] rounded-full -rotate-1 hover:rotate-0 transition-all duration-300">
      Outils que j’utilise
    </h2>
    <!-- Sous-texte -->
    <p class="max-w-xl mx-auto mb-16">
      Voici les technologies et outils que j’utilise régulièrement pour concevoir, développer et optimiser mes projets.
    </p>

    <!-- Grille des outils -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-6 gap-8 items-center justify-center">
      <!-- Exemple de bloc outil -->
      <div class="group flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2">
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/Adobe_Creative_Cloud_rainbow_icon.svg/langfr-280px-Adobe_Creative_Cloud_rainbow_icon.svg.png" alt="Adobe Suite" class="w-16 h-16 mb-3 drop-shadow-[0_0_10px_#36f4a4]/30 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
        <span class="text-sm">Adobe Suite</span>
      </div>

      <div class="group flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2">
        <img src="https://astro.build/assets/press/astro-icon-light.svg" alt="Astro" class="w-16 h-16 mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
        <span class="text-sm">Astro</span>
      </div>

      <div class="group flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2">
        <img src="https://cdn.worldvectorlogo.com/logos/shopify.svg" alt="Shopify" class="w-16 h-16 mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
        <span class="text-sm">Shopify</span>
      </div>

      <div class="group flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2">
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d5/Tailwind_CSS_Logo.svg" alt="Tailwind CSS" class="w-16 h-16 mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
        <span class="text-sm">Tailwind</span>
      </div>

      <div class="group flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2">
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/33/Figma-logo.svg" alt="Figma" class="w-16 h-16 mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
        <span class="text-sm">Figma</span>
      </div>

      <div class="group flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2">
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ef/ChatGPT-Logo.svg/langfr-330px-ChatGPT-Logo.svg.png" alt="ChatGPT" class="w-16 h-16 mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
        <span class="text-sm">ChatGPT</span>
      </div>

      <div class="group flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2">
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/98/WordPress_blue_logo.svg/1024px-WordPress_blue_logo.svg.png?20170312030453" alt="ChatGPT" class="w-16 h-16 mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
        <span class="text-sm">Wordpress</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
